VclsDrsEnabledClusterDeploymentModeAbsentAlarm.label="vSphere 集群服务已由 Retreat Mode 禁用。vSphere DRS 无法正常运行，vSphere HA 将无法以最佳方式运行"
VclsDrsEnabledClusterDeploymentModeAbsentAlarm.summary="警报，指示 DRS 已启用，但 vCLS 模式设置为 ABSENT"

### vCLS deploymentMode ABSENT with HA-enabled 和 DRS-disabled Alarm
VclsHaEnabledDrsDisabledClusterDeploymentModeAbsentAlarm.label="vSphere 集群服务已由 Retreat Mode 禁用。vSphere HA 将无法以最佳方式运行"
VclsHaEnabledDrsDisabledClusterDeploymentModeAbsentAlarm.summary="警报，指示 HA 已启用，DRS 已禁用，且 vCLS 模式设置为 ABSENT"

